.DT
lockout
Discworld player help
lockout

.SH Name
.SI 5
lockout - Lock yourself out of the game.
.EI

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
lockout <number of> <days|weeks> <reason>
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
On occassion some players may need some assistance in staying away
from Discworld during important times (such as exams).  The lockout
command allows you to lock yourself out of the game for a given
period.

Be very careful with this command, if you change your mind you cannot
undo the lockout.
.EP

.SH See also
.SI 5
.EI
